{"tid":921951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港男仔普遍都幾溫柔","createTime":"2018-11-30T03:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T16:11:32.000Z","uid":129459,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"02def958a946c520496203e60194d3f74ee8c773","tid":921951,"uid":129459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"我睇身邊朋友都係食住男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地會盡力滿足女友願望<br />\n只為令女友開心<br />\n不過有啲太誇張<br />\n<br />\n有位朋友要佢男友隨傳隨到<br />\n周不時又嫌佢窮(直頭同個男仔講)<br />\n女方總會因爲好多小事而嬲左個男仔<br />\nig,facebook唔準加女是基本<br />\n連現實生活都唔中意男友啲fd<br />\n要男友唔好同佢地接觸咁多...<br />\n但每次嗌交,最後都係男方認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而加都仲一齊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一個願打一個願挨<br />\n我局外人都唔會多咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己身邊識到嘅男仔都係<br />\n以前曖昧嗰啲,就算自己好攰,都會陪你傾到好夜<br />\n朋友嗰啲,又會好願意聽你講心事,甚至肯即刻岀黎同你傾<br />\n男友又會喺你需要佢嘅時候陪住你,氹你,仲會摸我個頭,去到邊都拖實你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7b619808c3bb2d22592b998e0a0bec900e74df","tid":921951,"uid":35187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"所以咪俾人玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86b96cc1860bfc724540ad583ab977a6a12a7bf","tid":921951,"uid":200297,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"唔係咁 你點會比佢屌？"},{"pid":"e609e1e1b0b4d60e48955078fb744b188bcf1d01","tid":921951,"uid":129459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd7b619808c3bb2d22592b998e0a0bec900e74df","tid":921951,"uid":35187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"所以咪俾人玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:41:12.000Z",